      "content": "i get what u mean about seeing a doctor but i'm really looking for something i can do right now so it doesnt get more uncomfortable. if i don't want to wait for an appointment, can i just use some of those antibiotic eye drops my friend has? would that be okay to use just for a day or two to see if it clears up? it's better to take action than to just do nothing, isn't it?",
